{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when the corresponding anchor location is used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Positive offset values indicate right and down, while negative values indicate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"left and up. Anchor locations may repeat, allowing the renderer to try multiple","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offsets to try and place a label using the same anchor.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When present, this property takes precedence over ","type":"text"},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"textVariableAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textRadialOffset"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"json","code":["{ \"text-variable-anchor-offset\": [\"top\", [0, 4], \"left\", [3,0], \"bottom\", [1,","1]] } "]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"top"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[0, 4]"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textOffset"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted down by 4 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When the renderer chooses the ","type":"text"},{"code":"left","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" anchor, "},{"code":"[3, 0]","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" will be used for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"textOffset","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"; the text will be shifted right by 3 ems.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This property is only applied to the style if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"text"},{"text":" is non-","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"symbolPlacement"},{"type":"text","text":" is set to an expression that evaluates to or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNSymbolPlacementPoint"},{"type":"text","text":". Otherwise, it is ignored."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"You can set this property to an expression containing any of the following:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Constant interleaved "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MLNTextAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"CGVector","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" array values"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Predefined functions, including mathematical and string operators"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Conditional expressions"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Variable assignments and references to assigned variables"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Interpolation and step functions applied to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"$zoomLevel"},{"text":" variable and\/or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"feature attributes"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnsymbolstylelayer\/textvariableanchoroffset"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}],"title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer\/textVariableAnchorOffset"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNSymbolStyleLayer"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"code":"textAnchor","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" locations, each paired with an offset value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use ","type":"text"},{"code":"textJustify: auto","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"justification based on anchor position.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","id